# Request Flow

This document explains how a request moves through the system.

---

## 🔄 Flow

1. User sends a request
2. Agent interprets intent
3. Agent selects API
4. API forwards to service
5. Service executes logic
6. Response returned to user

---

## 🧠 Example

User: "Get user data"

→ Agent decides action  
→ Calls API  
→ API calls service  
→ Service returns data  
→ Agent formats response
